Package: rpolycall
Type: Package
Title: R Binding for libpolycall
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Nnamdi Michael", "Okpala", email = "okpalan@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a thin registered native interface to the libpolycall
    configuration runner. The package forwards UTF-8 configuration paths and
    returns core status codes without implementing configuration or runtime logic.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: libpolycall (>= 1.5)
